<h1 class="kt-adv-heading38856_00addb-95 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading38856_00addb-95">Chewy Oatmeal Cookies</h1>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column38856_d2f4e3-9a kb-section-dir-horizontal single-post-header"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col">
<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image38856_bea764-09 size-thumbnail"><img data-perfmatters-preload decoding="async" width="150" height="150" src="https://joyfullymad.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/JM-headshot-square-600-150x150.jpg" alt="A woman with long brown hair wearing a gray shirt smiles in front of a background featuring green foliage and yellow fruit." class="kb-img wp-image-29295" srcset="https://joyfullymad.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/JM-headshot-square-600-150x150.jpg 150w, https://joyfullymad.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/JM-headshot-square-600-500x500.jpg 500w, https://joyfullymad.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/JM-headshot-square-600-360x360.jpg 360w, https://joyfullymad.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/JM-headshot-square-600-180x180.jpg 180w, https://joyfullymad.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/JM-headshot-square-600-96x96.jpg 96w, https://joyfullymad.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/JM-headshot-square-600.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px" fetchpriority="high"></figure>



