		<div class="wprm-recipe-summary wprm-block-text-normal"><span style="display: block;">These soft and chewy oatmeal cookies are a breeze to whip up and boast cinnamon, vanilla and oat flavors in every bite. They pair well with a cup of coffee or tea, and are also ideal for cookie trays.</span></div>
